<div class="get-involved-hero">
  <div class="center-text-wrapper margin-bottom-large">
    <h1>get involved</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="get-involved-flex-row">
    <div class="get-involved-img-wrapper"><img
        src="{{ 'collaborate.png' | asset_img_url: '500x' }}"
        loading="lazy"
        alt=""
        class="img-top-get-involved"></div>
    <div class="get-involved-flex-text">
      <h1 class="margin-b-15">collaborate</h1>
      <h2 class="margin-b-40 smaller-margin-mob">we believe in collaboration over competition</h2>
      <div class="general-text margin-b-20">Working with other artists, creators, and brands has been one way for us to empower each other. If you think your brand aligns with our values and are excited about being a part of what our artisans are doing in Kenya, reach out with your vision and we will get back to you as soon as possible.</div>
      <a
