        alt=""
        class="img-imani-experience"></div>
    <div class="involved-info-text-wrapper right-side give">
      <div class="big-medium-text margin-b-15">give</div>
      <div class="general-text margin-b-40">Walk alongside us as we fight to break the generational cycle of poverty in Kenya through holistic artisan empowerment. Our goal is to raise $100,000 by year-end to cover all expenses for our holistic programs, which are at the heart of our mission. Support our Artisans. Your generosity empowers.</div>
      <a href="https://imanicollective-ourimpact.org/donate" class="general-btn align-right center-mob w-inline-block"><img
          src="{{ 'blog_load-more.png' | asset_img_url: '250x' }}"
          loading="lazy"
          sizes="250px"
          alt=""
          class="btn-img">
        <div class="btn-text">DONATE</div>
      </a>
    </div>
